This is my portfolio website (aswling.com) where you can find some of my work. I made it from scratch with help from the following resources:

>Source Code Pro from Google Fonts (https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Source+Code+Pro)
>Responsive image gallery from Tania Rascia (https://www.taniarascia.com/how-to-build-a-responsive-image-gallery-with-flexbox/)
>JQuery Lightbox from from Saksham Mittal (https://github.com/saksham-mittal)
>Social icons from Font Awesome (http://fontawesome.io/)
>Tutorials by W3Schools (https://www.w3schools.com/default.asp)

Feel free to shoot me an email at alex@aswling.com if you want to chat about art, design, cute dogs, or anything else that interests ya!